data.description: This 2-story home offers a comfortable and spacious living experience with its 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. You'll be greeted by a great room with a built-in desk. The inviting open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and the chef's kitchen. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting high-end appliances, ample counter space, and modern fixtures. One of the standout features of this home is the finished basement, providing extra space for recreation. Upstairs, you'll find the primary suite, a tranquil retreat with its own private bath. The primary bath includes double vanity sinks, shower and a huge walk-in closet. For outdoor enthusiasts, the privacy-fenced yard ensures a sense of seclusion and security. Step out onto the cedar deck, where you can enjoy outdoor dining, entertaining guests, or simply relaxing in your own private outdoor oasis. This house combines modern amenities with comfort and privacy, making it a wonderful place to call home.  All information obtained from Seller and public records.
